name: AnExplorer VR File Manager
summary: AnExplorer VR Android File Manager is a simple, fast, and powerful file manager for Quest and Android devices. It helps you organise, transfer, and access files across internal storage, SD cards, USB drives, network shares, and cloud storages. It works across all Android devices including Meta Quest 2, Quest 3, Quest Pro, and other VR headsets, as well as phones, tablets, TVs, watches.
